title: Cooking vessel with decorative medallion

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a cooking vessel with a decorative medallion, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a is a bottom plan view of a cooking vessel with decorative medallion showing my new design;
FIG. 2 is a side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a bottom perspective view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a top plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 5 is a top perspective view thereof.
The broken line showings in FIGS. 1–5 are for illustrative purposes only, depicting the environment of the new design, forming no part thereof as claimed.
